OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778351318
OL,3,CMore than 200,000 migrants have
OL,4,Ccrossed the Channel in small boats
OL,5,Csince 2018
OL,7,FMore than 200,000 migrants have
OL,8,Farrived in the UK after crossing the
OL,9,FChannel since 2018, figures show.
OL,11,FDozens of migrants were seen being
OL,12,Fbrought ashore in Dover, Kent, on
OL,13,FFriday morning.
OL,15,FHome Office figures published on
OL,16,FSaturday confirm 70 people arrived in
OL,17,Fone boat that day.
OL,19,FThe latest crossings pushed the total
OL,20,Fnumber of arrivals since current
OL,21,Frecords began to 200,013.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/12
