CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778351318
OL,3,CMore than 200,000 migrants have
OL,4,Ccrossed the Channel in small boats
OL,5,Csince 2018
OL,7,FThe figure is calculated using the
OL,8,FGovernment's official statistics for
OL,9,F2018 to 2025 and provisional figures
OL,10,Frecorded so far this year.
OL,12,FJust over a third of the total, 72,094
OL,13,F(36%), have arrived since Labour took
OL,14,Fpower in July 2024, according to Press
OL,15,FAssociation analysis of Government
OL,16,Fdata.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
