OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778351318
OL,3,CMore than 200,000 migrants have
OL,4,Ccrossed the Channel in small boats
OL,5,Csince 2018
OL,7,FThe remaining 127,919 (64%) made the
OL,8,Fjourney under Conservative governments
OL,9,Fthat spanned four Tory prime
OL,10,Fministers: Theresa May, Boris Johnson,
OL,11,FLiz Truss and Rishi Sunak.
OL,13,FThe milestone comes after two women
OL,14,Fdied trying to make the journey on
OL,15,FSunday morning, following the deaths
OL,16,Fof six people reported in April by
OL,17,FFrench authorities.
OL,19,FChannel crossings so far in 2026 are
OL,20,Ftracking at a lower level than the
OL,21,Fprevious two years.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778351318
OL,3,CMore than 200,000 migrants have
OL,4,Ccrossed the Channel in small boats
OL,5,Csince 2018
OL,7,FThere have been 7,380 arrivals so far
OL,8,Fin 2026, 36% down on this point in
OL,9,F2025 and 16% below this stage in 2024.
OL,11,FSuccessive governments have tried to
OL,12,Fwork with France to disrupt crossings,
OL,13,Fas well as revising the rules for
OL,14,Fclaiming asylum in the UK in attempts
OL,15,Fto deter people from making the
OL,16,Fdangerous journey.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
