OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778351318
OL,3,CMore than 200,000 migrants have
OL,4,Ccrossed the Channel in small boats
OL,5,Csince 2018
OL,7,FIn April, Home Secretary Shabana
OL,8,FMahmood signed a three-year agreement
OL,9,Fwith French authorities to pay #662
OL,10,Fmillion to support beach patrols as
OL,11,Fpart of efforts to drive down arrivals.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, Ms Mahmood is seeking to
OL,14,Foverhaul the asylum system to deter
OL,15,Fcrossings and deport people easier,
OL,16,Fincluding proposed changes to make
OL,17,Frefugee status temporary.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
