OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778351318
OL,3,CMore than 200,000 migrants have
OL,4,Ccrossed the Channel in small boats
OL,5,Csince 2018
OL,7,FUnder the current Labour government,
OL,8,Fministers scrapped the Conservatives'
OL,9,Fmultimillion-pound deal to send
OL,10,Fmigrants who crossed the Channel from
OL,11,FFrance to Rwanda.
OL,13,FJust four volunteers were sent before
OL,14,Fthe policy was ditched.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778351318
OL,3,CMore than 200,000 migrants have
OL,4,Ccrossed the Channel in small boats
OL,5,Csince 2018
OL,7,FBut the move has prompted a legal
OL,8,Fbattle with the east African nation
OL,9,Fseeking to sue Britain for more than
OL,10,F#100 million claiming it has breached
OL,11,Fthe terms of the agreement and is owed
OL,12,Fmoney ` something lawyers for the UK
OL,13,Fdeny.
OL,15,FThe number of migrants making the
OL,16,Fjourney to the UK started at very low
OL,17,Flevels, with just 299 arrivals
OL,18,Frecorded in 2018.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778351318
OL,3,CMore than 200,000 migrants have
OL,4,Ccrossed the Channel in small boats
OL,5,Csince 2018
OL,7,FIn December of that year, then-home
OL,8,Fsecretary Sajid Javid cut short a
OL,9,FChristmas break to return to the UK
OL,10,Fand declared a "major incident" after
OL,11,F45 migrants crossed the Channel on
OL,12,FChristmas Day.
OL,14,FThe annual total increased to 1,843 in
OL,15,F2019, then to 8,466 in 2020, 28,526 in
OL,16,F2021 and 45,774 in 2022, which is the
OL,17,Fhighest number in a calendar year to
OL,18,Fdate.
OL,26,@rD@POUrD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778351318
OL,3,CMore than 200,000 migrants have
OL,4,Ccrossed the Channel in small boats
OL,5,Csince 2018
OL,7,FArrivals fell to 29,437 in 2023,
OL,8,Fbefore rising to 36,816 in 2024 and
OL,9,F41,472 in 2025.
OL,11,FWhile the volume of migrants reaching
OL,12,Fthe UK across the English Channel has
OL,13,Fvaried from year to year, there has
OL,14,Fbeen a steady increase since 2018 in
OL,15,Fthe number of people making the
OL,16,Fjourney per boat.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778351318
OL,3,CMore than 200,000 migrants have
OL,4,Ccrossed the Channel in small boats
OL,5,Csince 2018
OL,7,FThere were an average of seven
OL,8,Fmigrants per boat in 2018, rising to
OL,9,F11 in 2019, 13 in 2020, 28 in 2021, 41
OL,10,Fin 2022, 49 in 2023, 53 in 2024 and 62
OL,11,Fin 2025.
OL,13,FThe average so far in 2026 is 64.
OL,15,FThere is no official record of
OL,16,Ffatalities in the Channel but 2024 is
OL,17,Flikely to have been the deadliest
OL,18,Fyear, with 50 deaths recorded by the
OL,19,FFrench coastguard.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
